17906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:46:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c4c095268c45655cd6967a65658fbcd3f9127","tid":1539054,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"但問題係而家輸0:5 or 1:4<br />\n我寧願要0:5 然後攬炒"},{"pid":"e6240c7f2c487b7dd0d63c7fa489ea2bc9210755","tid":1539054,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJFfmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJFfmd.jpg&h=5166b6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa615608c169b3582311898775130c17482db436","tid":1539054,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7b670ffc65ccdfda3089ea26ead28219097d7e","tid":1539054,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n你有道理嘅話，係我個post都要推你個post"},{"pid":"9d3b3c081ca233e9a659e7a719add5404b41321f","tid":1539054,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7f44460af60700be71cbf481923be2955362f86","tid":1539054,"uid":56806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得每一個俾人拉，俾人打，為我地付出左前途、眼睛、生命嘅手足呀？<br />\n<br />\n同我發誓，無論付出幾大代價，都唔可以放過依個政權同佢嘅走狗<br />\n<br />\n時代革命&mdash;革命係無階段性嘅勝利，係最後一個敵人倒下之前，我地絕不放棄<br />\n<br />\n我地一齊黎，就要一齊走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"如果我地答應<br />\n我地死去的朋友唔會原諒我地"},{"pid":"6a93ecac5350d78a366c4baa39bf9b771f06d481","tid":1539054,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bde4700765199f1e78b5402b0699288dd3ee1b3","tid":1539054,"uid":42698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"罄竹難書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"我先用紙筆寫低，寫爆咗張紙"},{"pid":"5b27a8ab9728b7e28ca0d3ea09b3e36f1d810057","tid":1539054,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886bfbd054d31d0f5a0825c91795269abc142788","tid":1539054,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可！"},{"pid":"9b97d5f4a0